{"id":47,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":47,"title":"Chapter 44: Jesus Christ Blesses the Children","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 44","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 44"],["h1","Jesus Christ Blesses the Children"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_047_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p3"},"Jesus Christ told the Nephites to bring their little children to him. The children sat on the ground near Jesus."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.11-12"},"3 Nephi 17:11–12"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_047_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p5"},"The Savior told the people to kneel down. Then he knelt and prayed to Heavenly Father."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.13,15"},"3 Nephi 17:13, 15"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_047_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p7"},"The Savior’s prayer was so marvelous that it could not be written. It filled the Nephites with joy."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.15-17"},"3 Nephi 17:15–17"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_047_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p9"},"After his prayer Jesus said the Nephites would be blessed because of their faith."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.20"},"3 Nephi 17:20"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_047_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p11"},"He felt so much love and happiness that he wept."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.21"},"3 Nephi 17:21"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_047_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p13"},"Then he took the children and blessed each one. He prayed to Heavenly Father for them and wept again."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.21-22"},"3 Nephi 17:21–22"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_047_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p15"},"Jesus told the Nephites to look at their children."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.23"},"3 Nephi 17:23"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_047_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p17"},"As the people watched, angels came down from heaven and encircled the children. The children and the angels were surrounded by fire."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-44-jesus-christ-blesses-the-children.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/17.24"},"3 Nephi 17:24"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
